ECDSA signature verification

    Compile the ecc lib
    make 32  CC=dpu-upmem-dpurte-clang

    Check the dump file
    llvm-objdump -x  src/DPU/ecdsa_dpu > ecdsa_dpu.objdump

    Compile the DPU binary
    make 32  CC=dpu-upmem-dpurte-clang -C src/DPU/

Build params and pub key patterns
    Compile the ecc lib
    make 32  CC=dpu-upmem-dpurte-clang SW=1

    Check the dump file
    llvm-objdump -x  src/DPU/ecdsa_dpu > ecdsa_dpu.objdump

    Compile the DPU binary
    make 32  CC=dpu-upmem-dpurte-clang SW=1 -C src/DPU/

Execute the DPU binary
cd src/DPU/ && ./ecdsa_host  && cd -
